過唔係人人都放低到條道德線<br />\n而且PTBF應該要有D特質（靚仔或者講野識氹女仔）先做到<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話所有路數係符合我講既性價比既都對做果個人有一定要求(外在又好內在又好）<br />\n例如有D男仔係做part-time model"},{"pid":"67c5198c5c2e23b4db26fabbdfdbefe4cb2b1af0","tid":828834,"uid":84070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ee9ecf45c5fbaccecc38078282c6558f084ab8","tid":828834,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"咁易就冇窮人啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:46:58.000Z","msg":"窮人都有窮人既方法<br />\n例如做多幾份侍應/跟車<br />\n雖然我話呢D方法效率低<br />\n但關鍵係各施其力 盡力"},{"pid":"5536e8407e6cd237c486d32782ef705384ee9078","tid":828834,"uid":84070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f5a77b89547df7a84f3818a4eda01d5519f6441","tid":828834,"uid":8762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"用哂所有時間返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"你係話你已經用哂所有時間番工定建議人用哂所有時間番工？<br />\n前者既話咁你的確冇空閒再做其他野<br />\n後者既話現實係你加班唔會有錢收<br />\n亦都唔見得會升你先<br />\n所以先要搵其他路數"},{"pid":"3005535801284a53916a8b4ca628a1b03a37149c","tid":828834,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c5198c5c2e23b4db26fabbdfdbefe4cb2b1af0","tid":828834,"uid":84070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ee9ecf45c5fbaccecc38078282c6558f084ab8","tid":828834,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"咁易就冇窮人啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:46:58.000Z","msg":"窮人都有窮人既方法<br />\n例如做多幾份侍應/跟車<br />\n雖然我話呢D方法效率低<br />\n但關鍵係各施其力 盡力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"你估會唔會有人教你？"},{"pid":"fe3e2ea453e47e6f367a3c230bc27b20199b2825","tid":828834,"uid":114072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"對你份freelance有興趣 仲請唔請人"},{"pid":"58137f4c0ce18a0ba4a99f2c2bd789cda9942383","tid":828834,"uid":84070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3e2ea453e47